Package: zFactor
Type: Package
Title: Calculate the compressibility factor, Z, for hydrocarbons
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alfonso R. Reyes <alfonso.reyes@oilgainsanalytics.com>
Maintainer: Alfonso R. Reyes <alfonso.reyes@oilgainsanalytics.com>
Description: Computational algorithms to solve equations and find the
    compresibility factor (z). Correlations available: Hall-Yarborough, 
    Dranchuk-AbuKassem and Dranchuk-Purvis-Robinson. It uses the original 
    Standing-Katz chart for comparison and plotting.
Imports: rootSolve, tidyr, ggplot2, data.table
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown, testthat
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10)    
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
